OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. A few showers
OL,7,Fwill begin in the west around midday
OL,8,Fbefore spreading east through the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FScattered evening showers
OL,12,Fwill soon clear from the east leaving
OL,13,Fdry conditions and clear spells for a
OL,14,Ftime. Scattered showers will return
OL,15,Ftowards the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,18,Fscattered morning showers. Showers
OL,19,Fclear from the early afternoon before
OL,20,Fcloud and rain spread east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
